Jesus, Brooke, you're acting crazy again.
Don't you call me crazy. I am not crazy.

20:24.323 --> 20:25.688
I didn't call you crazy.
You just did.

20:25.757 --> 20:26.849
I didn't call you...
No, I didn't.

20:26.925 --> 20:28.893
I said you're acting crazy.
You know what, Gary?

20:28.961 --> 20:31.293
I asked you to do one thing
today, one very simple thing,

20:31.363 --> 20:33.456
