and you brought me three.

20:33.532 --> 20:36.695
God damn it. If I knew that it
was gonna be this much trouble,

20:36.768 --> 20:39.259
I would have brought home
24 lemons. Even 100 lemons.

20:39.338 --> 20:41.806
You know what I wish? I wish everyone
that was at that goddamn table

20:41.873 --> 20:43.397
had their own little private
bag of lemons.

20:43.475 --> 20:44.669
Honest to God! Gary,
it's not about the lemons.

20:44.743 --> 20:45.903
Well, that's all
you're talking about.

20:45.978 --> 20:48.446
I'm just saying it'd be nice
if you did things that I asked.

20:48.513 --> 20:52.279
