things without me having to ask you!

20:54.386 --> 20:57.480
Well, I do seem to remember doing
something for you this morning

20:57.556 --> 20:58.887
without you asking.

20:58.957 --> 21:01.323
Gary, come on.
What? I'm serious. Come here.

21:01.393 --> 21:03.327
You know what? I'm serious.
I really am. I am, too.

21:03.395 --> 21:06.592
Come on. You knew I was working
today and I made that meal.

21:06.665 --> 21:10.192
And you could have thought to
yourself, you know, you could have said,

21:10.269 --> 21:13.136
"Yeah, I think I'm gonna
get Brooke some flowers. "

21:13.372 --> 21:16.569
