that you don't like flowers,

21:16.642 --> 21:18.576
that they're a waste of money.

21:18.810 --> 21:20.072
Every girl likes flowers,
Gary.

21:20.145 --> 21:21.373
You said that you
don't like flowers.

21:21.446 --> 21:23.641
I'm supposed to take that to
mean that you do like flowers?

21:23.715 --> 21:26.479
No. This is not about... You're
not... God, you're not getting it.

21:26.551 --> 21:28.917
You're not getting this, Gary,
okay? It's not about the lemons.

21:28.987 --> 21:31.353
It's not about the flowers.
It's not about the dishes.

21:31.423 --> 21:34.824
It's just about... How many times do
I have to drop hints about the ballet?

21:34.893 --> 21:37.191
You know I can't stand...
Brooke, come here.

21:37.262 --> 21:40.595
We've talked about the damn
ballet. I hate the goddamn ballet!

21:40.666 --> 21:43.328
You got a bunch of dudes in tights
flopping around for three hours.

21:43.402 --> 21:45.336
It's like a medieval
techno show. It's a nightmare.

21:45.404 --> 21:47.065
I sit there in a sweat.
The whole thing, I do,

21:47.139 --> 21:49.232
wondering when the hell's the
goddamn nightmare gonna end.

21:49.308 --> 21:51.902
Go to a damn ballet. It's not
about you loving the ballet, Gary.

21:51.977 --> 21:54.172
It's about the person that
you love loves the ballet

21:54.246 --> 21:56.237
and you wanting to spend time
with that person.

21:56.315 --> 21:57.407
Not when they're
at the ballet.

21:57.482 --> 21:59.507
Okay. Forget the ballet!
Forget the ballet! I will.

21:59.584 --> 22:01.814
We don't go anywhere together.

22:02.754 --> 22:06.019
We just went to Ann Arbor
together. To Ann Arbor.

22:06.224 --> 22:08.215
To the
Michigan-Notre Dame game.

22:09.094 --> 22:13.724
You think screaming, drunk kids and
leprechauns doing backflips, that's fun.

22:13.799 --> 22:16.825
That's fun for me. Come
on, man. I did that for you.

22:16.902 --> 22:18.369
What do you...
How do you show up for me?

22:18.437 --> 22:21.099
I'm up on the bus
every goddamn day for you!

22:21.173 --> 22:22.765
Come on. You...
I'm busting my ass

22:22.841 --> 22:24.809
to be the best tour guide
in the damn city,

22:24.876 --> 22:26.935
so I can make enough money
to support both of us

22:27.012 --> 22:28.741
and hopefully you won't
have to work one day.

22:28.814 --> 22:30.975
I want to work.
All I ask, Brooke,

22:31.049 --> 22:33.142
is that you show a little bit
of appreciation.

22:33.218 --> 22:35.846
That I just get 20 minutes
to relax when I come home,

22:35.921 --> 22:39.584
instead of being attacked with
questions and nagged the whole damn time.

22:39.658 --> 22:42.456
You think that I nag you?
That's all you do!

22:42.561 --> 22:43.960
All you do is nag me!

22:44.029 --> 22:46.156
"The bathroom's a mess. "
"Your belt doesn't match. "

22:46.231 --> 22:48.222
"Hey, Gary, you should
probably go work out. "

22:48.300 --> 22:50.325
Nothing I ever do
is ever good enough!

22:50.402 --> 22:53.428
I just want to be left
the hell alone!

23:00.645 --> 23:02.806
Really? Is that
what you want, Gary?

23:02.881 --> 23:04.212
Is that what you want?
Yeah.

23:04.282 --> 23:05.306
That's what you want?
Yeah.

23:05.384 --> 23:07.249
